    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Multiplayer games where each player has a form or card with numbers. The numbers can be crossed out or indicated when the number drawn by the game master is on this form. There are also variants with colors and figures instead of numbers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000202/RKD</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000119919/RKD-Nederlands Instituut voor Kunstgeschiedenis [database] (2021-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Spellen voor meerdere spelers, waarbij iedere speler een formulier of kaart met getallen heeft. De getallen kunnen worden weggestreept of aangeduid wanneer het getal, dat wordt getrokken door de spelleider, op dit formulier staat. Er bestaan ook varianten met kleuren en figuren i.p.v. getallen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
